  <brief_title>The Effect of Administration of Low Dose Adrenaline During Surgery on Bleeding During Hip Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Intraoperative Low Dose Adrenaline on Bleeding in Total Hip Arthroplasty - a Randomized Placebo-controlled Trial</official_title>
